# StyLua reads this like .gitignore. It does NOT read .gitignore itself,
# so the exclusions below must mirror the relevant parts of that file.
#
# Rule of thumb: any .lua under src/dlc/UI/ whose name does NOT start
# with CivVAccess_ is a base-game file we ship verbatim. Reformatting it
# would diverge from upstream and make re-diffing after a Civ V patch
# painful. Don't touch them.

# Base-game frontend screens (paired with our CivVAccess_*Access wrappers)
